Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.23,0:29:23.46,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}just how much longer you have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.72,0:29:25.91,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Lying under...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.51,0:29:31.74,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The clouds of fear that refuse to flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.23,0:29:34.81,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Tears of indigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.73,0:29:39.30,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You don't have to cry no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.65,0:29:44.20,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Hey, it's time for us to go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.87,0:29:47.42,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}A mother's standing here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.48,0:29:50.84,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}before your very eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.99,0:29:56.91,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's time you found her...\Nit's time you found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.13,0:30:02.35,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}A shelter from the cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.77,0:30:05.31,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}A mother's standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.65,0:30:11.60,OP j,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's time you found her...\Nit's time you found her.
